edu.xtec.jclic.report

Class Reporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.xtec.jclic.report.Reporter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JDBCReporter, TCPReporter

    public class Reporter
extends Object
    This class implements the basic operations related with the process of the results obtained by users playing JClic activities. These operations include users identification, compilation of data coming from the activities, storage of this data for a posterior use and presentation of summarized results.
    Version:
    13.09.10
    Author:
    Francesc Busquets (fbusquets@xtec.cat)
